---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Working Capital Loan - Short Term Business Financing | TrueCred Loan Expert">

<!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <a href="#">Loans</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <span>Working Capital Loan</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Working Capital Loan</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Keep your business running smoothly with working capital loans designed for operational expenses, inventory management, and seasonal cash flow needs. Get flexible credit from ₹2 lakhs to ₹1 crore with interest rates starting at 12% p.a.</p>
      <div class="hero-highlights">
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-indian-rupee-sign"></i>
          <span>Loan Amount: ₹2L - ₹1 Cr</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-calendar-days"></i>
          <span>Tenure: 6 Months - 3 Years</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-percent"></i>
          <span>Interest: 12% onwards</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page Content -->
  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content-main">
          <h2>What is a Working Capital Loan?</h2>
          <p>A working capital loan is a short-term financing solution that helps businesses cover their day-to-day operational costs such as rent, salaries, raw material purchase, inventory stocking, utility bills, and other routine expenses. Unlike term loans used for expansion or asset purchase, working capital loans bridge the gap between receivables and payables, ensuring your business never faces a cash crunch during high-demand seasons or delayed payment cycles.</p>
          <p>TrueCred Loan Expert offers multiple working capital financing options including overdraft facilities, cash credit, invoice discounting, and short-term term loans from over 35 lenders. Our platform analyses your business cash flow cycle and recommends the most cost-effective working capital solution. Whether you're a manufacturer waiting for receivables, a retailer stocking up for festive season, or a service provider managing monthly payroll, we have the right product for you.</p>

          <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-box">
              <span class="info-value">12%</span>
              <span class="info-label">Interest Rate (p.a.)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-box">
              <span class="info-value">₹1 Crore</span>
              <span class="info-label">Max Loan Amount</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-box">
              <span class="info-value">3 Years</span>
              <span class="info-label">Max Tenure</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>Working Capital Loan Interest Rates — April 2026</h3>
          <table class="rate-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Bank / NBFC</th>
                <th>Interest Rate (p.a.)</th>
                <th>Processing Fee</th>
                <th>Max Tenure</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>SBI</td>
                <td>12.00% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 1.00%</td>
                <td>3 Years</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>HDFC Bank</td>
                <td>12.50% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 2.00%</td>
                <td>3 Years</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>ICICI Bank</td>
                <td>13.00% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 2.25%</td>
                <td>2 Years</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Bajaj Finserv</td>
                <td>14.00% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 2.50%</td>
                <td>3 Years</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>FlexiLoans</td>
                <td>15.00% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 2.00%</td>
                <td>2 Years</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>

          <h3>Eligibility Criteria</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Business operational for at least 2 years with consistent revenue</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Minimum annual turnover of ₹10,00,000 for unsecured working capital</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Business owner or authorized signatory aged between 25 and 65 years</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> CIBIL score of 700+ (personal) for the business owner/promoter</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> GST registration and regular filing for at least 12 months</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Positive cash flow with manageable existing debt obligations</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>How to Get a Working Capital Loan</h3>
          <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">1</div>
              <h4>Assess Cash Flow Gap</h4>
              <p>Analyze your business cash flow cycle — identify when payments come in and when expenses are due to determine the right loan amount.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">2</div>
              <h4>Choose Product Type</h4>
              <p>Select from overdraft, cash credit, invoice discounting, or term loan based on your usage pattern and repayment flexibility needs.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">3</div>
              <h4>Submit Financials</h4>
              <p>Upload bank statements, GST returns, and receivables/payables data for quick assessment by our partner lenders.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">4</div>
              <h4>Access Funds</h4>
              <p>Get a credit limit or lump sum disbursed within 48-72 hours. Repay flexibly based on the product type chosen.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>Documents Required</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Business registration and GST registration certificate</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Last 12-24 months bank statements showing business cash flow</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Latest 12 months GST returns (GSTR-3B and GSTR-1)</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Debtor and creditor aging reports for invoice discounting</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Audited financial statements for the last 2 years (if available)</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> KYC documents of promoters/directors — Aadhaar, PAN, and address proof</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="content-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-file-signature"></i> Get Working Capital Loan</h3>
            <form class="sidebar-form" onsubmit="return false;">
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" class="form-input" placeholder="Full Name" required>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="tel" class="form-input" placeholder="Mobile Number" maxlength="10" required>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <select class="form-input" required>
                  <option value="" disabled selected>Loan Amount</option>
                  <option value="200000">₹2,00,000</option>
                  <option value="500000">₹5,00,000</option>
                  <option value="1000000">₹10,00,000</option>
                  <option value="2000000">₹20,00,000</option>
                  <option value="3000000">₹30,00,000</option>
                  <option value="5000000">₹50,00,000</option>
                  <option value="10000000">₹1,00,00,000</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" class="form-input" placeholder="City" required>
              </div>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">
                Apply Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-link"></i> Quick Links</h3>
            <div class="sidebar-links">
              <a href="/pages/business-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Business Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/home-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Home Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/loan-against-property"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Loan Against Property</a>
              <a href="/pages/gold-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Gold Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/education-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Education Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/car-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Car Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/credit-cards"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Credit Cards</a>
              <a href="/pages/credit-score"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Credit Score</a>
              <a href="/pages/calculators"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> EMI Calculator</a>
              <a href="/pages/insurance"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Insurance</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">Got Questions?</span>
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p>Common questions about working capital loans.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            What is the difference between a working capital loan and a term loan?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              A working capital loan is for short-term operational needs (6 months to 3 years) and can be revolving (overdraft/cash credit) where you draw and repay as needed. A term loan is for specific purposes like equipment purchase or expansion with a fixed repayment schedule over a longer tenure (3-7 years). Working capital loans have flexible usage; term loans often have end-use restrictions.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            What types of working capital financing are available?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Common types include: (a) Cash Credit/Overdraft — revolving facility against stock/debtors, (b) Short-term Term Loan — lump sum with fixed EMIs, (c) Invoice Discounting — advance against unpaid invoices, (d) Letter of Credit — for import transactions, (e) Bank Guarantee — for contract/bid requirements. TrueCred helps you choose the most suitable type based on your business needs.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Can seasonal businesses get working capital loans?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Yes, several lenders on TrueCred specialize in financing seasonal businesses like agriculture, tourism, retail, and festival-dependent industries. These loans are structured with flexible repayment schedules that align with your revenue cycle — lower EMIs during lean months and higher EMIs during peak seasons. Show your historical seasonal patterns through bank statements to get optimized terms.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Is collateral required for working capital loans?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Unsecured working capital loans are available up to ₹50 lakhs to ₹1 crore from most lenders based on business performance. For larger amounts, lenders may require collateral such as property, stock, receivables, or FD. CGTMSE-backed loans up to ₹2 crore are collateral-free for eligible MSMEs. Secured working capital facilities generally come at lower interest rates.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            How quickly can I get a working capital loan?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Fintech lenders on TrueCred can process working capital loans in 24-48 hours for businesses with strong digital footprints. Bank overdraft and cash credit facilities may take 5-10 business days for the initial setup. Invoice discounting platforms can advance funds within 24 hours against uploaded invoices. Once set up, revolving facilities provide instant access to funds.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page CTA -->
  <section class="page-content" style="padding-top:0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-cta">
        <div>
          <h3>Keep Your Business Cash Flow Healthy</h3>
          <p>Get flexible working capital financing from ₹2L to ₹1 Cr. Apply now and access funds within 48 hours.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline" style="color:#fff;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:14px 32px;font-size:0.95rem;">
          Apply Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->

</BaseLayout>
